data.description: Welcome to this beautifully updated 5 bed, 3 full bath home in High Point Estates. Sitting on 3/4 acre this beautiful home backs up to a nature conservancy with lots of privacy. Upon entering, find yourself in the grand foyer with a large closest for storage. The fully updated kitchen includes painted cabinets, new hardware, quartz countertops. The living room directly off the kitchen is sure to impress w grand 30' ceilings, tons of natural light & beautiful fireplace. Main level also features a dining room, sitting room full bathroom & bedroom. On the second level the grand master suite features a beautiful tray ceiling & attached bathroom w a huge closet. Bedroom 3 and 4 are connected by a jack-n-jill bath. Large 3.5 attached car garage allows for plenty of storage! Don't miss out
